                                fugit culpa nihil vero?
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="~/images/Grow-Trees-On-the-path-to-environment-sustainability-login.png"
                             alt="Second slide">
                        <div class="carousel-caption d-block d-none d-sm-block">
                            <h5>Second</h5>
                            <p>
                                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nisi ratione culpa suscipit quo
                                est quod consequuntur temporibus velit sunt amet repellat, repudiandae explicabo
                                reiciendis facere ea architecto. Inventore, iure qui?
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="~/images/Grow-Trees-On-the-path-to-environment-sustainability-login.png"
                             alt="Third slide">
                        <div class="carousel-caption d-block d-none d-sm-block">
                            <h5>Third</h5>
                            <p>
                                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Officiis quae sunt ut voluptate
                                ratione excepturi esse recusandae consequuntur corporis nisi blanditiis omnis qui
                                asperiores expedita, laborum autem saepe. Enim, corrupti?
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div id="form" class="col-lg-4">
                <form asp-area="User" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Login" class="my-auto">
                    
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">Email address</label>
                        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="InputEmail1" aria-describedby="emailHelp"
                               placeholder="evan.donohue@gmail.com">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label mt-2">Password</label>
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="InputPassword1" placeholder="User@123">
                    </div>
                    <button id="LoginBtn" class="btn btn-primary col-12 py-0" type="submit">Login</button>

                    <div class="lostNewAcc">
                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="" style="font-size: 12px">Lost your password?</a>
                        <p id="newPass">Don't have an account? <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Registration">Create an account</a></p>
                    </div>

                </form>
                <div class="PP text-center mx-auto">
                    <p> <a href="">Privacy Policy</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>